<rss version="2.0" xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/"><channel><title>战区</title><link>https://www.twz.com</link><description>防御世界的强大进攻。</description><lastBuildDate>Fri, 24 Apr 2026 09:08:39 GMT</lastBuildDate><generator>rfeed v1.1.1</generator><docs>https://github.com/svpino/rfeed/blob/master/README.md</docs><item><title>Saildrone 携带导弹的 Spectre 参加海军中型无人船竞赛</title><link>https://www.twz.com/sea/saildrones-missile-toting-spectre-enters-navys-medium-sized-unmanned-ship-competition</link><description>&lt;p&gt;Saildrone 与国防巨头联手，扩大其经过验证的车辆概念，并为其配备导弹和潜艇搜索传感器。&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt; &lt;a href="https://www.twz.com/sea/saildrones-missile-toting-spectre-enters-navys-medium-sized-unmanned-ship-competition"&gt;Saildrone 携带导弹的“幽灵”号参加海军中型无人舰艇竞赛的&lt;/a&gt;帖子首先出现在&lt;a href="https://www.twz.com"&gt;《战区》&lt;/a&gt;上。&lt;/p&gt;</description><pubDate>Thu, 23 Apr 2026 23:18:10 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.twz.com/sea/saildrones-missile-toting-spectre-enters-navys-medium-sized-unmanned-ship-competition</guid></item><item><title>特朗普对伊朗小船下达杀戮令（更新）</title><link>https://www.twz.com/news-features/trump-puts-out-kill-order-on-irans-small-boats</link><description>&lt;p&gt;特朗普还表示，他将把海峡的排雷工作增加“三倍”，尽管目前还不清楚这些活动目前正在进行什么（如果有的话）。&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;a href="https://www.twz.com/news-features/trump-puts-out-kill-order-on-irans-small-boats"&gt;特朗普对伊朗小船下达杀戮令（更新）的&lt;/a&gt;帖子首先出现在&lt;a href="https://www.twz.com"&gt;“战区”&lt;/a&gt;上。&lt;/p&gt;</description><pubDate>Thu, 23 Apr 2026 22:54:50 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.twz.com/news-features/trump-puts-out-kill-order-on-irans-small-boats</guid></item><item><title>NASA 777 飞行实验室降落在兰利</title><link>https://www.twz.com/air/nasas-777-flying-laboratory-touches-down-at-langley</link><description>&lt;p&gt;NASA 最大的研究飞机将接替该机构标志性的 DC-8，并计划于 2027 年进行首次测试。&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt; &lt;a href="https://www.twz.com/air/nasas-777-flying-laboratory-touches-down-at-langley"&gt;NASA 777 飞行实验室降落在兰利的&lt;/a&gt;帖子首先出现在&lt;a href="https://www.twz.com"&gt;“战区”&lt;/a&gt;上。&lt;/p&gt;</description><pubDate>Thu, 23 Apr 2026 20:55:52 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.twz.com/air/nasas-777-flying-laboratory-touches-down-at-langley</guid></item><item><title>海军急忙用地狱火导弹武装航母战斗群</title><link>https://www.twz.com/sea/rush-to-arm-carrier-strike-groups-with-hellfire-missiles-for-anti-drone-defense-disclosed-by-navy</link><description>&lt;p&gt;随着单向攻击无人机日益增长的威胁，海军正在为其舰队提供更多的反无人机硬杀伤能力。&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt; &lt;a href="https://www.twz.com/sea/rush-to-arm-carrier-strike-groups-with-hellfire-missiles-for-anti-drone-defense-disclosed-by-navy"&gt;海军用地狱火导弹冲向航母战斗群&lt;/a&gt;后，首先出现在&lt;a href="https://www.twz.com"&gt;战区&lt;/a&gt;。&lt;/p&gt;</description><pubDate>Thu, 23 Apr 2026 18:04:00 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.twz.com/sea/rush-to-arm-carrier-strike-groups-with-hellfire-missiles-for-anti-drone-defense-disclosed-by-navy</guid></item><item><title>伊朗袭击改变了海军在中东加油的方式</title><link>https://www.twz.com/sea/iranian-attacks-change-way-navy-refuels-its-ships-in-middle-east</link><description>&lt;p&gt;美国海军创建了一种商业“油轮跑步机”，用于在海上给加油机加注，提供的经验教训可能会对未来的行动产生更大的影响。&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt; &lt;a href="https://www.twz.com/sea/iranian-attacks-change-way-navy-refuels-its-ships-in-middle-east"&gt;伊朗袭击后改变了海军在中东加油的方式&lt;/a&gt;首先出现在&lt;a href="https://www.twz.com"&gt;战区&lt;/a&gt;。&lt;/p&gt;</description><pubDate>Thu, 23 Apr 2026 16:41:00 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.twz.com/sea/iranian-attacks-change-way-navy-refuels-its-ships-in-middle-east</guid></item><item><title>特朗普停火延期后，伊朗加大对霍尔木兹海峡船只的攻击力度（更新）</title><link>https://www.twz.com/news-features/iran-ramps-up-attacks-on-ships-in-the-strait-of-hormuz-after-trump-ceasefire-extension</link><description>&lt;p&gt;由于伊朗拒绝承诺进行和谈，停火的未来仍然存在疑问。&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt; &lt;a href="https://www.twz.com/news-features/iran-ramps-up-attacks-on-ships-in-the-strait-of-hormuz-after-trump-ceasefire-extension"&gt;特朗普停火延期后伊朗加大对霍尔木兹海峡船只的攻击力度（更新）&lt;/a&gt;首先出现在&lt;a href="https://www.twz.com"&gt;战区&lt;/a&gt;。&lt;/p&gt;</description><pubDate>Thu, 23 Apr 2026 00:07:53 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.twz.com/news-features/iran-ramps-up-attacks-on-ships-in-the-strait-of-hormuz-after-trump-ceasefire-extension</guid></item><item><title>我们刚刚了解到的有关特朗普级战列舰计划的所有新消息</title><link>https://www.twz.com/sea/everything-new-we-just-learned-about-the-trump-class-battleship-program</link><description>&lt;p&gt;我们正在更清楚地了解海军如何使用这些舰艇，每艘舰艇的估计成本为 17B 美元。&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt; &lt;a href="https://www.twz.com/sea/everything-new-we-just-learned-about-the-trump-class-battleship-program"&gt;我们刚刚了解到的有关特朗普级战列舰计划的一切新消息&lt;/a&gt;首先出现在&lt;a href="https://www.twz.com"&gt;“战区”&lt;/a&gt;上。&lt;/p&gt;</description><pubDate>Wed, 22 Apr 2026 23:25:26 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.twz.com/sea/everything-new-we-just-learned-about-the-trump-class-battleship-program</guid></item><item><title>新型低成本巡航导弹具有类似战斧的射程</title><link>https://www.twz.com/air/new-raacm-er-low-cost-cruise-missile-features-tomahawk-like-range</link><description>&lt;p&gt;RAACM-ER 巡航导弹的射程超过 1,000 海里，旨在以更低的成本射程更远。&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;a href="https://www.twz.com/air/new-raacm-er-low-cost-cruise-missile-features-tomahawk-like-range"&gt;具有类似战斧射程的新型低成本巡航导弹&lt;/a&gt;后首次出现在&lt;a href="https://www.twz.com"&gt;战区&lt;/a&gt;。&lt;/p&gt;</description><pubDate>Wed, 22 Apr 2026 20:16:38 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.twz.com/air/new-raacm-er-low-cost-cruise-missile-features-tomahawk-like-range</guid></item><item><title>美国海军 MH-60S 飞行员在海鹰巡演期间谈论多任务角色</title><link>https://www.twz.com/sponsored-content/u-s-navy-mh-60s-pilot-talks-multi-mission-roles-during-tour-of-the-seahawk</link><description>&lt;p&gt;品牌内容：MH-60S 是真正的美国海军主力，从执行舰艇补给到水雷搜寻再到反水面战。&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt; &lt;a href="https://www.twz.com/sponsored-content/u-s-navy-mh-60s-pilot-talks-multi-mission-roles-during-tour-of-the-seahawk"&gt;美国海军 MH-60S 飞行员在海鹰巡演期间谈论多任务角色&lt;/a&gt;首先出现在&lt;a href="https://www.twz.com"&gt;战区&lt;/a&gt;。&lt;/p&gt;</description><pubDate>Wed, 22 Apr 2026 19:33:12 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.twz.com/sponsored-content/u-s-navy-mh-60s-pilot-talks-multi-mission-roles-during-tour-of-the-seahawk</guid></item><item><title>美国空军的 F-15EX 购买量刚刚增加一倍，这非常有意义</title><link>https://www.twz.com/air/f-15ex-buy-was-just-doubled-by-the-usaf-which-makes-perfect-sense</link><description>&lt;p&gt;虽然它最初是取代 F-15C，但更多的 F-15EX 将为老化的 F-15E 攻击鹰和可能的其他类型提供现成的继任者。&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;a href="https://www.twz.com/air/f-15ex-buy-was-just-doubled-by-the-usaf-which-makes-perfect-sense"&gt;美国空军将 F-15EX 的购买量增加了一倍，这非常有意义，&lt;/a&gt;首先出现在&lt;a href="https://www.twz.com"&gt;《战区》&lt;/a&gt;上。&lt;/p&gt;</description><pubDate>Wed, 22 Apr 2026 18:38:10 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.twz.com/air/f-15ex-buy-was-just-doubled-by-the-usaf-which-makes-perfect-sense</guid></item></channel></rss>